@startmindmap
* Windows Credentials\nProtection
** Password hygiene
*** Length 10 / admin 12
*** Passphrases
*** Password managers
** LAPS
*** Unique local admin pw\nper machine
*** Auto-renewal via GPO
*** Stored in AD, ACL-guarded
** Logon types
*** Type 2/7/10/11 cache creds
*** Type 3 (network) does not
*** Prefer WMI / WinRM /\nPowerShell remoting
** Reduce in-memory secrets
*** Disable WDigest\n(UseLogonCredential=0)
*** Audit ID 4776 first
** LSA Protection
*** RunAsPPL = 1
*** Protected Process
*** Bypass: signed kernel\ndriver (mimidrv.sys)
** Credential Guard
*** VBS isolates LSA secrets
*** LSAIso in a separate VM
*** Needs UEFI / VT / TPM /\nEnterprise
** Account discipline
*** Privileged accounts\nonly for DC tasks
*** Protected Users group\n(Kerberos-only, no NTLM,\nno delegation, 4h TGT)
@endmindmap
